# Netlify Redirects for React SPA (React Router)
# All routes fall back to index.html so React Router handles them client-side.

# Force HTTPS (handled by Netlify automatically, but explicit here for docs)
# http://burhanuddinmoriswala.netlify.app/* https://burhanuddinmoriswala.netlify.app/:splat 301!

# Redirect www → non-www (update if your custom domain uses www)
# http://www.yourdomain.com/* https://yourdomain.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback — MUST be last
/*    /index.html    200
